{
  "id": "Vxx0xTH6",
  "slug": "chatplugin",
  "title": "ChatPlugin",
  "description": "A feature-rich and modular chat ecosystem, lightweight and efficient by design.",
  "body": "![ChatPlugin banner](https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/chatplugin-banner.png)\n\n<a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/website-wiki.png\" alt=\"Website & wiki\" title=\"Visit ChatPlugin's website\"></a><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/spacer-22p.png\" alt=\"Spacer\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/eSnAPhvMTG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/discord-server.png\" alt=\"Discord server\" title=\"Join the Discord server\"></a><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/spacer-22p.png\" alt=\"Spacer\"><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/getting-started/Premium-version\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/premium-version.png\" alt=\"Premium version\" title=\"View information about the premium version\"></a>\n<br>\n\nChatPlugin is a highly customizable and modular plugin that lets you personalize not only the chat, but many other aspects of your server as well. It also offers several Staff modules to make server administration easier.\n\nYou can click on the highlighted links to learn more about each feature. For additional details, please visit [the website](https://remigio07.me/chatplugin).\n\n<center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<th>\n<br><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/minecart-with-command-block.png\" alt=\"Minecart with Command Block\">\n\n⚡Versatile, powerful<br>all-in-one solution\n\n<small>\n<a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Chat</a>, <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/GUIs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GUIs</a>, <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">join-quit modules</a>,\nserver customization and more.\n</small>\n</th>\n<th>\n<br><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/knowledge-book.png\" alt=\"Knowledge Book\">\n\nℹ️ Extensive wiki and comprehensive support\n\n<small>\nDetailed <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">guides</a> available; fast,\nfriendly support via <a href=\"https://discord.gg/eSnAPhvMTG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Discord</a>.\n</small>\n</th>\n<th>\n<br><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/feather.png\" alt=\"Feather\">\n\n⚖️ Lightweight and modular design\n\n<small>\nTurn off what you do not need:\nChatPlugin is fully modular.\n</small>\n</th>\n<th>\n<br><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/redstone-comparator.png\" alt=\"Redstone Comparator\">\n\n⚙️ Vast but concise developer API\n\n<small>\nEasily integrate with the robust\nand 100% documented <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/development/API\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">API</a>.\n</small>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center>\n<br>\n\n![Showcase header](https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/showcase-header.png)\n\n**Premium version**  \nThe premium version is also _proxy-compatible_ and includes the plugin's most advanced features. _Non-exclusive_ list:\n\n<center>\n<small>\n<table style=\"text-align: center; border-width: 1px; border-spacing: 1px;\">\n<tr>\n<th><strong>Module</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Features</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Description</strong></th>\n<th><strong>In-game footage</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Scoreboards\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Scoreboards</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>flickerless, asynchronous</li>\n<li>custom <font color=\"#FF5555\">red numbers</font> (1.20.3+)</li>\n<li>only-zeros mode (all versions)</li>\n<li>event-triggered scoreboards</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Scoreboards#scoreboard-command\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/scoreboard</a></code> to toggle</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Displays useful, animated and fully customizable information in the player's sidebar with unlimited scoreboards.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/scoreboards.gif\" alt=\"Scoreboards footage\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#hover-info\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Hover info</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>clickable profiles and <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#player-ping\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><font color=\"#55FFFF\">@mentions</font></a></li>\n<li>Discord-like <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#instant-emojis\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">:clickable_emojis:</a> ➝ 🙂</li>\n<li>URLs <font color=\"#55FFFF\"><u>highlighting</u></font></li>\n<li>show ranks' descriptions on hover</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Shows interactive information when players hover over chat messages and executes actions if they click them.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/hover-info.gif\" alt=\"Hover info footage\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Bossbars\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Bossbars</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>8 <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Bossbars#colors\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">colors</a> and 6 <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Bossbars#styles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">styles</a></li>\n<li>animation while <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Bossbars#loading-bossbar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">loading</a></li>\n<li>legacy mode for 1.7 and 1.8 players</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Bossbars#bossbar-command\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/bossbar</a></code> to toggle</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Displays ads or useful and easily readable information using unlimited, fully customizable bossbars.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/bossbars.gif\" alt=\"Bossbars footage\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#chat-log\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Chat log</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>filter by sender, text or date</li>\n<li>option to show only private or blocked messages</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#chatlog-command\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/chatlog</a></code> to check</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Logs public and <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#private-messages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">private messages</a> to the storage, enabling Staff members to search them using filtering queries.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/chat-log.png\" alt=\"Chat log screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Punishments\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Punishments</a> (beta)</strong></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>4 additional GUIs:\n<ul>\n<li>Banlist GUI</li>\n<li>Warnlist GUI</li>\n<li>Mutelist GUI</li>\n<li>Player punishments GUI</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#anti-ban-evading-system\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">anti ban evading system</a></li>\n</ul></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Punishments#bans\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bans</a>, <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Punishments#banwaves\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">banwaves</a>, <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Punishments#warnings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">warnings</a>, <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Punishments#kicks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kicks</a>, <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Punishments#mutes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mutes</a> and soon™ a web interface.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/punishments.png\" alt=\"Punishments screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#account-check\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Account check</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#anti-ban-evading-system\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">detect and auto-ban alt accounts</a></li>\n<li>geo-based detection</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#accountcheck-command\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/accountcheck</a></code> to check a player's history</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Check if a player owns multiple accounts using several techniques, including <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/IP-lookup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IP lookups</a>, to get a reliable result.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/account-check.png\" alt=\"Account check screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Integrations#anticheats\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Anticheat integrations</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>2 additional GUIs:\n<ul>\n<li>Violations GUI</li>\n<li>Player violations GUI</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>supported anticheats:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://matrix.rip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Matrix</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vulcanac.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vulcan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Elikill58/Negativity\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Negativity</a></li>\n<li>‼️more added upon request</li>\n</ul>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Real-time alerts and info about player violations, seamlessly integrated with the anticheat installed.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/anticheat-integrations.gif\" alt=\"Anticheat integrations screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Discord-integration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Discord integration</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>9 slash commands</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Discord-integration#discordmessage-command\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/discordmessage</a></code> to send messages from Minecraft</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Check the server's status and punishments, perform <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/IP-lookup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IP lookups</a> and receive notifications on Discord.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/discord-integration.png\" alt=\"Discord integration screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Telegram-integration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Telegram integration</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>9 commands</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Telegram-integration#telegrammessage-command\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/telegrammessage</a></code> to send messages from Minecraft</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Check the server's status and punishments, perform <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/IP-lookup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IP lookups</a> and receive notifications on Telegram.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/telegram-integration.png\" alt=\"Telegram integration screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/MoTDs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>MoTDs</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Languages#language-detection\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">automatic language detection</a></li>\n<li>custom MoTD if the player is banned</li>\n<li>custom MoTD if on an outdated version</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Custom MoTDs with placeholder support translated using the player's language.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/motds.png\" alt=\"MoTDs screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</small>\n</center>\n<br>\n\n**Free version**  \nMost features are included with the free version. _Non-exclusive_ list:\n\n<center>\n<small>\n<table style=\"text-align: center; border-width: 1px; border-spacing: 1px;\">\n<tr>\n<th><strong>Module</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Features</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Description</strong></th>\n<th><strong>In-game footage</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Chat</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#formatted-chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">formatted chat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#chat-channels\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">chat channels</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#antispam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">antispam</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#player-ping\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><font color=\"#55FFFF\">@mentions</font></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#private-messages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">private messages</a></li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#player-ignore\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/ignore</a></code></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#instant-emojis\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">:instant_emojis:</a> ➝ 🙂</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>All-in-one chat system with channels, advanced antispam protection, player @mentions, private messaging and :instant_emojis:.</td>\n<td>\n<img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/antispam.gif\" alt=\"Antispam footage\">\n<img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/chat.gif\" alt=\"Chat footage\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/GUIs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>GUIs</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>6 built-in GUIs (12 on the premium version):\n<ul>\n<li>Main GUI</li>\n<li>Player info GUI</li>\n<li>Preferences GUI</li>\n<li>Languages GUI</li>\n<li>Chat color GUI</li>\n<li>Emojis' tone GUI</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li>deeply customizable</li>\n<li>animated (auto-refresh)</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Quickly customize preferences, monitor real-time stats and access key information at a glance.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/guis.gif\" alt=\"GUIs footage\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Join-quit</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Languages#language-detection\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">automatic language detection</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#join-messages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">join messages</a> and <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#join-titles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">titles</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#quit-messages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">quit messages</a> (+ <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#switch-messages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">switch</a> on the premium version)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Join-quit#suggested-version\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">suggest recommended version</a></li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Fully customizable rank-based join/quit messages and titles, plus alerts for outdated clients.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/join-quit-switch-messages.gif\" alt=\"Join/quit/switch messages footage\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Server customization</strong></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Tablists\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">tablists</a> (<a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Tablists#custom-suffix\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">yellow number</a> on the premium version)</li>\n<li>clickable <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">actionbars</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/F3-server-names\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">F3 server names</a></li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Enhance your server's visuals with custom tablists, actionbars, F3 server branding and clickable advertisements.</td>\n<td>\n<img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/tablists.gif\" alt=\"Tablists footage\">\n<img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/f3-server-name.gif\" alt=\"F3 server name footage\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/IP-lookup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>IP lookup</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>accurate and fast</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/IP-lookup#load-on-join-option\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">load-on-join</a> option for <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Languages#language-detection\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">automatic language detection</a></li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Geolocate players' IPv4 addresses with precision.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/ip-lookup.png\" alt=\"IP lookup screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Chat#staff-chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Staff chat</strong></a></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li>quick communication among Staff members</li>\n<li>cross-server on the premium version</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Simple Staff-only chat which includes the console.</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/staff-chat.png\" alt=\"Staff chat screenshot\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Performance metrics</strong></td>\n<td><ul>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Ping\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/ping</a></code> to check a player's ping</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/TPS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/tps</a></code> to check the server's ticks per second</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/MSPT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">/mspt</a></code> to check the server's milliseconds per tick</li>\n</ul></td>\n<td>Analyze latencies, tick rates and responsiveness using colors to represent performance levels.</td>\n<td>\n<img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/ping.png\" alt=\"Ping screenshot\">\n<img src=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/common/mspt.png\" alt=\"MSPT screenshot\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</small>\n</center>\n<br>\n\n![Integrations header](https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/assets/marketplaces/modrinth/integrations-header.png)\n\nChatPlugin offers integrations with the following plugins:\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/SirBlobman/CombatLogX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**CombatLogX**</a>: prevents vanished players from hitting others\n- <a href=\"https://discordsrv.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**DiscordSRV**</a>: blocks messages when a player cannot use the chat\n- <a href=\"https://essentialsx.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**EssentialsX**</a>: adds the `{balance}` placeholder, even without a placeholder plugin\n- <a href=\"https://geysermc.org/wiki/floodgate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Floodgate**</a>: detects Bedrock players to adapt certain features\n- <a href=\"https://gadgetsmenu.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**GadgetsMenu**</a>: removes cosmetics when a player enables vanish\n- <a href=\"https://geysermc.org/wiki/geyser\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Geyser**</a>: detects Bedrock players to adapt certain features\n- <a href=\"https://luckperms.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**LuckPerms**</a>: checks permissions even when players are offline\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/Maximvdw/MVdWPlaceholderAPI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**MVdWPlaceholderAPI**</a>: enables other plugins' placeholders and offers <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Placeholders\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">100+ custom placeholders</a>\n- <a href=\"https://placeholderapi.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**PlaceholderAPI**</a>: enables other plugins' placeholders and offers <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Placeholders\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">100+ custom placeholders</a>\n- <a href=\"https://wiki.rosewooddev.io/PlayerParticles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**PlayerParticles**</a>: removes particles when a player enables vanish\n- <a href=\"https://protocolsupport.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**ProtocolSupport**</a>: detects players' versions to send certain version-based messages\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/UltraCosmetics/UltraCosmetics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**UltraCosmetics**</a>: removes cosmetics when a player enables vanish\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/milkbowl/Vault\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Vault**</a>: adds the `{balance}` placeholder, even without a placeholder plugin\n- <a href=\"https://viaversion.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**ViaVersion**</a>: detects players' versions to send certain version-based messages\n\nAdditionally, the premium version integrates with the following plugins:\n- <a href=\"https://matrix.rip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Matrix**</a>: provides the Violations and the Player violations GUI\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/Elikill58/Negativity\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Negativity**</a>: provides the Violations and the Player violations GUI\n- <a href=\"https://vulcanac.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Vulcan**</a>: provides the Violations and the Player violations GUI\n- <a href=\"https://enginehub.org/worldguard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**WorldGuard**</a>: adds the `region-enter` and the `region-leave` event-triggered <a href=\"https://remigio07.me/chatplugin/wiki/modules/Scoreboards\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">scoreboards</a>",
